Content: Hey!  Would you like to tryout for the official RHK Clan in Fortnite? If so_ then here are the requirements. If you meet the requirements then you  can tryout_ those requirements will be included as well.  First_ this is a Nintendo Switchtm clan only.  Second_ you must have a mic and play on NAE Servers.  Win requirement_ 100 wins altogethercrown_ Now if you meet those requirements_ then you can chose to tryout DM RHK_FreshShibeツ#0111 or  RHKDarkCatツ#5487.  The tryout consists of build fights_ edit course and real games.  If you succeed you must change you name on FNBR and on Discord_ it will be RHK(Your chosen name)  And we have a official discord if you join the clan. Clan games included.  Hopefully you can join and lastly_ Good luck_ Have fun!
